<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1939_09_19_an_OffenerBrief"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> Offener Brief, 19. 9. 1939</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <editionStmt n="bw2"> <edition>2. Auflage</edition> </editionStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Original in The Rush Rhees Archives, Swansea, Sig: SU/PC/1/4.</p> <p>Abschrift und Kommentar Gabriel Citron, Scan in BA. </p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>Transcribed by <persName role="editor" full="yes">Gabriel Citron</persName></item><item>2010/05/31: letter added</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><facsimile> <graphic url="images/facsimiles/b1939_09_19_an_OffenerBrief_f001.jpg"/> </facsimile><text><body><div type="transcript" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"> <div org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="center"><hi rend="underline">Testimonial</hi></p> </div> <div type="maintext" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p>I have known Mr. R. Rhees for 4 years; he has attended my lectures on philosophy and we have had a great many discussions both on philosophical and general subjects. I have always been strongly impressed by the great seriousness and intelligence with which he tackles any problem.</p> <p rend="indent">Mr. Rhees is an exceptionally kind and helpful man and will spare no trouble to assist his students.</p> <p rend="indent">His German is very good indeed.</p> </div> <div type="salute" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="indent">Ludwig Wittgenstein</p> </div> <div type="salute" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p>Trinity College, </p> <p>Cambridge, </p> <p>19th September, 1939. </p> </div> </div></body></text></TEI>